UID:4LaoIs8Z9pdC0AVk2jQj6
SUMMARY:Washed in Black (Pearl Jam) w/ Jar of Flies (Alice in Chains) | Ann
	ual 90's Tribute Show w/ Two of Seattle's Best!
DTSTAMP:20260318T152742Z
DTSTART:20260531T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Time for the annual Tribute to the 90s s Best!$20 Advance | $28
	 DOS | 21+~Washed In Black - A Tribute to Pearl Jam~Jar of Flies - The Ult
	imate AIC ExperienceAn extremely rare bill..... our schedules dont often a
	lign for full sets & we are all super stoked! A show not to miss! Relive s
	ome memories\, join with friends\, & make new ones of both. Come on out to
	 the historic Tractor Tavern and help us Make America Grunge Again - Salud
